1.1
log
@Initial revision
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: main.c,v 1.7 2001/11/19 19:02:18 mpech Exp $	*/
/*	$NetBSD: main.c,v 1.6 1996/02/08 20:45:01 mycroft Exp $	*/

